Value: Satellite and receiver clock products derived from analysis of Global Navigation Satellite System (GNSS) data. These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International GNSS Service (IGS) and combined by the IGS analysis coordinator to form the official IGS final clock product (weekly).
Recommendation: 1. Recommend removing "the" before "generated" in the second sentence:

"These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International GNSS Service (IGS) and combined by the IGS analysis coordinator to form the official IGS final clock product (weekly)."

2. Recommend providing additional information about the spatial and temporal coverage of the data (i.e. is coverage global? what is the pixel resolution? when did data coverage start and is it ongoing?)
